                    <img src="~/images/3.jpg" alt="3" class="img-responsive" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/images/4.jpg" alt="4" class="img-responsive" />
                    <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #808080;">
                Nursing education in Australia currently teaches undergraduate nursing students’
                basic digital literacy skills but is yet to
                implement e-health literacy, such as health informatics,
                into the undergraduate Bachelor of Nursing curricula.
            </p>

            <hr style="margin-left: 150px; margin-right: 150px; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px;">

            <p style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; color: #808080;">
                <a style="color:#1a8cff;" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="About">About</a>
                <br>
                <a style="color:#1a8cff;" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Researcher">Researchers</a>
                <br>
                <a style="color:#1a8cff;" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Participate">Participate</a>

            </p>

            <hr style="margin-left: 150px; margin-right: 150px; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px;">

            <p style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #808080;">
                For further information on the program, please refer to About Page (Above) or contact Annette Stunden by email at A.Stunden@westernsydney.edu.au
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
